    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-biofluid-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. The assessment team concludes that the model is fit for the intended use as described in the package narrative.",
